1
00:01:23,127 --> 00:01:30,583
<i>[Weaving A Tale of Love 2]</i>

2
00:01:32,059 --> 00:01:36,023
<i>[Episode 7]</i>

3
00:01:36,815 --> 00:01:38,295
The journey to the Xizhou is far and long,

4
00:01:39,015 --> 00:01:40,975
I don't know how much trouble you've caused

5
00:01:40,975 --> 00:01:42,955
or how long His Majesty will keep you there,

6
00:01:42,955 --> 00:01:44,655
So, if there's enough time,

7
00:01:44,655 --> 00:01:46,675
after I get things done in the Luoyang estates,

8
00:01:46,675 --> 00:01:48,155
I'd like to visit uncle, auntie,

9
00:01:48,155 --> 00:01:49,655
my foster mother, grandpa, and Shun,

10
00:01:51,015 --> 00:01:53,855
I also want to say goodbye to Lady Wu,

11
00:01:53,855 --> 00:01:55,015
Will you allow me to go or not?

12
00:01:58,535 --> 00:01:59,535
You little downy bird,

13
00:02:00,735 --> 00:02:01,855
I can't hide anything from you

14
00:02:04,175 --> 00:02:06,135
Lady Wu is affectionate and loyal to you,

15
00:02:07,855 --> 00:02:09,135
Naturally, you should go and see her,

16
00:02:13,295 --> 00:02:18,095
By the way, why don't you ask why I was demoted

17
00:02:19,255 --> 00:02:21,755
and why was I banished to Xizhou?

18
00:02:21,755 --> 00:02:23,275
Wait until these matters are settled,

19
00:02:23,275 --> 00:02:25,435
I'll surely give you a thorough interrogation,

20
00:02:25,435 --> 00:02:27,735
You'll have to explain everything to me,

21
00:02:29,215 --> 00:02:31,815
Xizhou is extremely perilous and savage,

22
00:02:33,495 --> 00:02:34,775
Are you truly willing to go with me?

23
00:02:34,775 --> 00:02:36,275
What do you mean by this?

24
00:02:36,275 --> 00:02:37,535
You are my husband,

25
00:02:37,535 --> 00:02:38,575
I am your wife,

26
00:02:38,575 --> 00:02:40,975
Wherever you go, I should go too,

27
00:02:45,535 --> 00:02:46,935
Why are you doing this? Put me down!

28
00:02:48,015 --> 00:02:49,215
Wherever I go, you shall go too,

29
00:02:49,935 --> 00:02:51,655
Now, your husband is going to bed

30
00:02:52,295 --> 00:02:53,895
Naturally, you should go to bed with me,

31
00:02:55,055 --> 00:02:56,415
This time, you cannot escape,

32
00:03:08,615 --> 00:03:10,775
The Crown Prince has just sent a message,

33
00:03:10,775 --> 00:03:13,135
stating that His Majesty issued a decree
during the court,

34
00:03:13,855 --> 00:03:16,175
For privately discussing imperial matters,
Pei Shouyue has been demoted

35
00:03:17,135 --> 00:03:18,695
to the Senior Official of Xizhou,

36
00:03:19,575 --> 00:03:20,832
I am extremely sorry!

37
00:03:22,215 --> 00:03:23,552
Keep talking!

38
00:03:24,295 --> 00:03:25,995
Pei Shouyue thanked His Majesty on the spot,

39
00:03:25,995 --> 00:03:28,695
Great! Excellent!

40
00:03:29,495 --> 00:03:31,975
This… this is really self-inflicted,

41
00:03:32,575 --> 00:03:34,055
Word came from the palace that

42
00:03:34,055 --> 00:03:35,855
His Majesty was greatly angered last night

43
00:03:35,855 --> 00:03:38,015
and ordered Pei Shouyue to set off tomorrow

44
00:03:38,015 --> 00:03:39,375
with no delay,

45
00:03:39,895 --> 00:03:42,495
It can be seen that he is utterly discarded,

46
00:03:43,295 --> 00:03:44,575
Pei Shouyue's residence

47
00:03:44,575 --> 00:03:47,655
is probably turned into complete chaos by now,

48
00:03:49,095 --> 00:03:52,775
I wonder if they can attend to the transfer
of the Luoyang estates,

49
00:03:53,895 --> 00:03:56,055
Just a few days ago, Liuli told me

50
00:03:56,575 --> 00:03:57,855
no credit

51
00:03:57,855 --> 00:03:59,455
or monetary settlement is allowed,

52
00:04:01,055 --> 00:04:02,055
I bet at this moment

53
00:04:02,575 --> 00:04:04,895
she must be eager for us
to settle with gold and silver,

54
00:04:04,895 --> 00:04:07,415
Otherwise, the 200,000 strings of cash

55
00:04:07,415 --> 00:04:11,455
could cost her numerous carriages and manpower
to transport to Xizhou,

56
00:04:17,175 --> 00:04:18,495
You simpleton,

57
00:04:19,375 --> 00:04:21,935
Are you still thinking about sending her money?

58
00:04:23,095 --> 00:04:25,095
Who said I'm going to give her that much money?

59
00:04:28,775 --> 00:04:30,135
Pei Shouyue

60
00:04:30,855 --> 00:04:32,055
has lost his mind now,

61
00:04:32,055 --> 00:04:35,015
He has even offended his two backers,

62
00:04:36,575 --> 00:04:38,255
As for Kudi Liuli,

63
00:04:39,015 --> 00:04:41,755
without Lady Wu being her backer,

64
00:04:41,755 --> 00:04:43,915
she is just a fish on the chopping board,

65
00:04:43,915 --> 00:04:46,495
Why should I give her 200,000 strings of cash?

66
00:04:48,495 --> 00:04:50,375
As for the Pei family of Zhongjuan,

67
00:04:52,695 --> 00:04:55,015
now that Pei Xingjian is down,

68
00:04:55,975 --> 00:04:58,935
who among them dares to confront me?

69
00:05:05,575 --> 00:05:06,695
Madam is so wise

70
00:05:10,858 --> 00:05:16,785
<i>[Fortuitous Tranquility]</i>

71
00:05:19,744 --> 00:05:20,815
My lord,

72
00:05:20,815 --> 00:05:23,055
this is the invitation sent by Madam Yang
from the Wu's Mansion

73
00:05:24,416 --> 00:05:24,979
<i>[Invitation from Wu's Mansion]</i>

74
00:05:24,979 --> 00:05:27,360
<i>[Presenting to Lord Pei,
Shouyue, please come to appreciate tea,]</i>

75
00:05:33,735 --> 00:05:35,095
No need to follow,

76
00:05:35,095 --> 00:05:36,935
If Madam asks, tell her I've gone
to the county office,

77
00:06:07,036 --> 00:06:08,842
<i>[Mother of Lord Wu, Madam Yang]</i>

78
00:06:14,775 --> 00:06:16,815
Greetings to Madam Yang from Xingjian,

79
00:06:20,055 --> 00:06:23,095
Shouyue, you are a clever person,

80
00:06:23,895 --> 00:06:25,535
I do not like to beat around the bush,

81
00:06:26,815 --> 00:06:29,375
The Pei and Wu families have been friends
for many years,

82
00:06:30,015 --> 00:06:32,255
I have always regarded you as a close nephew,

83
00:06:33,335 --> 00:06:34,415
All these years,

84
00:06:35,335 --> 00:06:39,455
Lady Wu has also looked out for you and Liuli,

85
00:06:39,975 --> 00:06:41,655
To speak presumptuously

86
00:06:42,455 --> 00:06:45,415
without Lady Wu's mediation and planning,

87
00:06:47,095 --> 00:06:50,855
Liuli might have lost her life long ago,

88
00:06:51,975 --> 00:06:55,895
and you two would never have the chance
to tie the knot,

89
00:07:10,135 --> 00:07:14,135
Now, Lady Wu needs assistance,

90
00:07:15,015 --> 00:07:16,535
You have won the Emperor's deep favor,

91
00:07:17,535 --> 00:07:21,255
You are capable to help Lady Wu,

92
00:07:26,015 --> 00:07:29,095
Yet how can you be so ungrateful,

93
00:07:29,095 --> 00:07:31,015
and even adding insult to injury?

94
00:07:34,855 --> 00:07:37,095
It truly bitterly disappointing,

95
00:07:38,375 --> 00:07:40,015
The Wu family has always treated me
with great kindness,

96
00:07:41,935 --> 00:07:44,855
My spouse and I have also been greatly favored
by Lady Wu,

97
00:07:46,215 --> 00:07:47,495
We dare not forget her magnanimity,

98
00:07:47,495 --> 00:07:49,815
What about the deeds you have done recently

99
00:07:51,455 --> 00:07:55,455
and the words you said to His Majesty
in the palace last night?

100
00:07:56,215 --> 00:08:00,535
Is that how you should treat a benefactor?

101
00:08:01,575 --> 00:08:04,935
Princess said you and Shouyue will go westward,

102
00:08:04,935 --> 00:08:06,695
without knowing how many years will pass
before you can return,

103
00:08:07,215 --> 00:08:11,095
So naturally,
the properties in Luoyang have to be sold,

104
00:08:12,015 --> 00:08:14,895
But it's not convenient
to carry so much money and silk,

105
00:08:16,455 --> 00:08:18,735
Princess is worried about you,

106
00:08:18,735 --> 00:08:23,015
so she has packed up a couple of boxes
of gold and silver utensils for you,

107
00:08:23,015 --> 00:08:24,215
making it convenient for you to carry,

108
00:08:24,815 --> 00:08:26,315
These boxes of gold and silver

109
00:08:26,315 --> 00:08:30,015
roughly worth over 10,000 strings of cash,

110
00:08:30,655 --> 00:08:32,375
Why don't you take it first?

111
00:08:32,935 --> 00:08:36,415
The rest can be given to you
after you return from Xizhou,

112
00:08:36,935 --> 00:08:37,935
What do you think?

113
00:08:39,015 --> 00:08:40,935
Princess's concerns are very valid,

114
00:08:40,935 --> 00:08:43,395
Shouyue and I are currently bearing guilt,

115
00:08:43,395 --> 00:08:46,295
Even 10,000 strings of cash, I'm afraid,
might bring disaster,

116
00:08:46,295 --> 00:08:49,175
Since you have not yet prepared the money,

117
00:08:50,535 --> 00:08:52,955
I will not trouble Princess then,

118
00:08:52,955 --> 00:08:55,175
It's okay not to sell this manor,

119
00:08:55,695 --> 00:08:56,975
Before leaving Chang'an,

120
00:08:56,975 --> 00:09:00,175
I will hand over the lands and stores
to the clan for safekeeping,

121
00:09:01,735 --> 00:09:03,015
What do you mean by this?

122
00:09:03,575 --> 00:09:04,695
Are you going back on your word?

123
00:09:05,575 --> 00:09:07,815
Liuli, I am warning you,

124
00:09:08,575 --> 00:09:11,615
Shouyue already offended His Majesty
and Lady Wu,

125
00:09:12,375 --> 00:09:14,055
Since you no longer have a backer,

126
00:09:14,575 --> 00:09:16,495
you better be even more sensible,

127
00:09:17,415 --> 00:09:19,395
If you comply with the Princess's wishes,

128
00:09:19,395 --> 00:09:20,975
in the future, Princess

129
00:09:20,975 --> 00:09:25,055
will not just watch you and Shouyue grow old
and die in that barbaric land,

130
00:09:26,215 --> 00:09:29,095
Otherwise, you'll both suffer the consequences,

131
00:09:34,215 --> 00:09:35,535
Shouyue,

132
00:09:36,495 --> 00:09:39,215
I forgive you for being irrational
in a thoughtless moment,

133
00:09:39,775 --> 00:09:44,095
If you're willing to make amends
before His Majesty for this matter

134
00:09:44,095 --> 00:09:48,115
and pave the way
for Lady Wu's elevation to Empress,

135
00:09:48,115 --> 00:09:52,855
Lady Wu and I will remain eternally grateful,

136
00:09:56,775 --> 00:09:58,775
Madam, please calm down,

137
00:09:58,775 --> 00:10:00,224
If it's a personal matter,

138
00:10:00,935 --> 00:10:02,815
when Lady Wu needs my help

139
00:10:03,655 --> 00:10:05,295
I will definitely exert my utmost effort

140
00:10:05,895 --> 00:10:08,335
to repay Lady Wu's favor to me and Liuli,

141
00:10:08,855 --> 00:10:10,015
But regarding the matter
of establishing the Empress,

142
00:10:10,855 --> 00:10:12,535
it's not a personal or familial matter,

143
00:10:12,535 --> 00:10:13,555
but a state affair,

144
00:10:13,555 --> 00:10:15,735
It's a matter of great importance
to the nation's foundation,

145
00:10:16,335 --> 00:10:17,415
I dare not

146
00:10:20,295 --> 00:10:22,275
and will not jeopardize public interests
for personal reasons,

147
00:10:22,275 --> 00:10:25,015
I speak to you with kind words and good intent,

148
00:10:26,415 --> 00:10:29,935
yet you respond with sanctimonious
and self-righteous reprimands,

149
00:10:31,015 --> 00:10:32,655
Your implication

150
00:10:33,655 --> 00:10:38,895
is that Lady Wu doesn't deserve
to be the Empress, right?

151
00:10:46,895 --> 00:10:49,655
I understand the Princess's meaning,

152
00:10:50,415 --> 00:10:52,215
Then, 10,000 strings of cash it is,

153
00:10:53,095 --> 00:10:54,095
But I need you to promise me one thing,

154
00:10:54,695 --> 00:10:56,235
When delivering gold and silver

155
00:10:56,235 --> 00:10:59,775
my uncles and aunts from the Pei family
of Zhongjuan must also be present,

156
00:10:59,775 --> 00:11:00,775
Why?

157
00:11:01,655 --> 00:11:03,295
I swore an oath in public that

158
00:11:04,095 --> 00:11:06,495
the assets of Luoyang will never be used
for my own family,

159
00:11:06,495 --> 00:11:07,815
otherwise, I won't meet a good end,

160
00:11:08,775 --> 00:11:11,815
Therefore,
how much money Princess can gather right now

161
00:11:11,815 --> 00:11:13,295
is not important,

162
00:11:13,295 --> 00:11:17,135
but I can't let the aunts in the clan suspect
that I have embezzled it for my own use,

163
00:11:18,175 --> 00:11:19,655
It is better to do this sooner than later,

164
00:11:20,375 --> 00:11:21,775
How about this?

165
00:11:21,775 --> 00:11:22,775
Tomorrow morning,

166
00:11:22,775 --> 00:11:25,535
I will then invite the aunts
to witness the transaction in the Temple,

167
00:11:26,615 --> 00:11:28,335
No matter if Princess takes it over

168
00:11:28,335 --> 00:11:29,635
or not,

169
00:11:29,635 --> 00:11:32,815
I will bring the contracts
for the fields and shops there,

170
00:11:33,375 --> 00:11:35,055
If no one is willing to buy them at that time,

171
00:11:35,615 --> 00:11:38,615
I will just have them serve
as ancestral properties,

172
00:11:41,095 --> 00:11:45,335
Good, I will pass on your message to Princess,

173
00:11:58,055 --> 00:12:00,495
My lady, what do you plan to do?

174
00:12:07,295 --> 00:12:08,544
No rush,

175
00:12:11,095 --> 00:12:12,175
Let me think it over,

176
00:12:25,415 --> 00:12:26,575
I want to ask you again,

177
00:12:27,255 --> 00:12:30,615
You might act ungratefully
and stand against Lady Wu,

178
00:12:31,575 --> 00:12:36,335
but are you not afraid
of the thunderous wrath of His Majesty

179
00:12:37,015 --> 00:12:39,255
and even disregard your own future prospects?

180
00:12:40,135 --> 00:12:42,655
I receive the ruler's salary,
so I share the ruler's concerns,

181
00:12:44,255 --> 00:12:45,935
To make the country prosperous
and to safeguard people's peace life

182
00:12:46,575 --> 00:12:48,135
are all I ever wanted to achieve,

183
00:12:48,736 --> 00:12:49,815
I have no regrets,

184
00:12:49,815 --> 00:12:51,264
What about Liuli then?

185
00:12:58,695 --> 00:13:00,735
She is your newly wedded wife,

186
00:13:01,335 --> 00:13:03,575
She wholeheartedly wishes
to spend the rest of her life with you,

187
00:13:05,455 --> 00:13:07,975
The environment in Xizhou is harsh and cold,

188
00:13:09,375 --> 00:13:14,095
Could you bear to see her suffer with you

189
00:13:14,775 --> 00:13:17,495
and even lose her life?

190
00:13:21,055 --> 00:13:23,495
Considering the years of bonding
between our two families,

191
00:13:24,335 --> 00:13:28,455
this is my last reminder for you,

192
00:13:28,455 --> 00:13:31,135
Thank you for your reminder, Madam,

193
00:13:47,815 --> 00:13:49,375
To be the Senior Official of Xizhou?

194
00:13:50,135 --> 00:13:52,295
Do you think it is a comfortable position?

195
00:13:52,295 --> 00:13:53,375
<i>[Su's Residence]</i>

196
00:13:53,375 --> 00:13:55,255
The current situation there is complicated,

197
00:13:56,495 --> 00:14:00,575
Many previous governors have been there,
and none of them achieved good results,

198
00:14:00,575 --> 00:14:02,335
Shouyue knew this,

199
00:14:03,455 --> 00:14:05,088
Now,

200
00:14:05,895 --> 00:14:10,155
The Protector-General Qu of Xizhou is
from the royal lineage of Gaochang,

201
00:14:10,155 --> 00:14:11,415
He has deep roots,

202
00:14:12,615 --> 00:14:15,415
Shouyue's position, Senior Official,
ranks just below him,

203
00:14:17,535 --> 00:14:19,335
I fear that misfortune outweighs fortune,

204
00:14:21,855 --> 00:14:22,975
It's all your fault,

205
00:14:24,175 --> 00:14:26,935
Why did you ask for an imperial order
to go on another expedition to Western Regions?

206
00:14:28,855 --> 00:14:31,255
Shouyue is also as stubborn as a mule

207
00:14:32,415 --> 00:14:35,735
You, as a master, have gone to the West
on multiple expeditions,

208
00:14:35,735 --> 00:14:37,575
How can he just sit idly by?

209
00:14:39,135 --> 00:14:40,615
Even so,

210
00:14:40,615 --> 00:14:43,375
Shouyue is too freewheeling,

211
00:14:44,095 --> 00:14:46,815
Why doesn't he consider Liuli at all?

212
00:14:48,655 --> 00:14:51,335
You men want to achieve success,

213
00:14:51,335 --> 00:14:53,015
so you can only see the advantages,

214
00:14:54,055 --> 00:14:55,855
Although Liuli is unyielding and staunch

215
00:14:56,615 --> 00:14:58,975
her body is actually quite weak,

216
00:14:59,495 --> 00:15:01,455
Shouyue knew this,

217
00:15:04,855 --> 00:15:07,975
All right, stop crying now,

218
00:15:07,975 --> 00:15:10,175
In a while, Shouyue will come over
to bid us goodbye,

219
00:15:10,695 --> 00:15:11,995
Don't let him hear that,

220
00:15:11,995 --> 00:15:13,695
I want him to hear that,

221
00:15:14,975 --> 00:15:16,735
Xizhou is windy and dusty,

222
00:15:17,535 --> 00:15:19,895
I'm afraid Liuli might be blown away
as soon as she steps out the door there,

223
00:15:21,375 --> 00:15:23,435
Besides, didn't you just say

224
00:15:23,435 --> 00:15:26,635
there is more danger than safety
for Shouyue's journey to Xizhou?

225
00:15:26,635 --> 00:15:28,935
What if Liuli gets implicated?

226
00:15:30,255 --> 00:15:32,175
We might as well let him go his own way

227
00:15:32,175 --> 00:15:33,735
and keep Liuli in Chang'an,

228
00:15:34,495 --> 00:15:37,055
At least we can keep her safe and sound,

229
00:15:38,055 --> 00:15:41,535
When Shouyue returns,
they can naturally reunite,

230
00:15:44,815 --> 00:15:48,015
But what if Shouyue doesn't return?

231
00:15:54,375 --> 00:15:56,015
If Shouyue doesn't return

232
00:15:56,615 --> 00:15:58,935
he shouldn't even bring Liuli with him,

233
00:15:59,975 --> 00:16:02,335
General, have you forgotten about Luqi?

234
00:16:03,495 --> 00:16:06,035
Do you want Liuli to become the next Luqi

235
00:16:06,035 --> 00:16:07,975
and die for Shouyue?

236
00:16:16,775 --> 00:16:19,335
<i>The environment in Xizhou is harsh and cold,</i>

237
00:16:20,495 --> 00:16:25,575
<i>Could you bear to see her suffer with you</i>

238
00:16:26,215 --> 00:16:28,695
<i>and even lose her life?</i>

239
00:16:29,775 --> 00:16:34,095
You're the one who's dragging your family down,

240
00:16:34,655 --> 00:16:38,535
Liuli is not entirely innocent either,

241
00:16:39,895 --> 00:16:42,855
As husband and wife, you are one,

242
00:16:43,615 --> 00:16:47,015
Since you were the first to be ungrateful
and treacherous,

243
00:16:48,175 --> 00:16:50,775
don't blame me for being ruthless,

244
00:16:51,895 --> 00:16:55,255
I've heard that His Majesty was furious

245
00:16:56,055 --> 00:16:58,735
and ordered you to assume your position
without delay,

246
00:16:59,655 --> 00:17:01,175
In my opinion,

247
00:17:02,215 --> 00:17:04,815
you need not prepare any other luggage,

248
00:17:05,775 --> 00:17:10,215
just bring two coffins with you,

249
00:17:41,856 --> 00:17:42,975
Put it over here,

250
00:17:42,975 --> 00:17:44,855
Ni, pack all of these,

251
00:17:45,655 --> 00:17:47,360
Everything is packed,

252
00:17:48,975 --> 00:17:50,735
How did the books of Shouyue end up here?

