00:36:07,135 --> 00:36:11,895
Meeting you today can be considered destiny,

496
00:36:12,655 --> 00:36:15,055
Lady Wu sent someone to tell me

497
00:36:16,175 --> 00:36:19,975
that you intend to sell the Luoyang estates
at a low price,

498
00:36:20,895 --> 00:36:22,055
She also said

499
00:36:22,055 --> 00:36:25,495
Princess intends to help you,

500
00:36:26,095 --> 00:36:28,675
Unfortunately, she doesn't have enough money
at the moment,

501
00:36:28,675 --> 00:36:32,275
I have managed to gather 20,000 taels of gold

502
00:36:32,275 --> 00:36:34,215
to help you out a little,

503
00:36:37,135 --> 00:36:38,775
With my status,

504
00:36:39,415 --> 00:36:44,055
Princess,
do you think I can take over this property?

505
00:36:48,615 --> 00:36:52,215
Madam Yang is
of distinguished and honorable family history,

506
00:36:52,215 --> 00:36:54,015
You are also the birth mother of Lady Wu,

507
00:36:55,015 --> 00:36:57,015
Who dares say that you can't?

508
00:36:57,775 --> 00:37:00,735
Even His Majesty would disagree
with that person if he knew,

509
00:37:02,335 --> 00:37:04,315
Pei Shouyue just offended Lady Wu,

510
00:37:04,315 --> 00:37:06,895
Why would Lady Wu help her? Is she mad?

511
00:37:07,535 --> 00:37:09,095
So what if there's a grudge?

512
00:37:09,095 --> 00:37:12,455
It would be crazy not
to take such a great advantage,

513
00:37:14,295 --> 00:37:17,735
Uncles and aunts,
thank you for witnessing today's transaction,

514
00:37:17,735 --> 00:37:19,335
I am very grateful,

515
00:37:29,375 --> 00:37:30,935
May all uncles and aunts bear witness,

516
00:37:32,015 --> 00:37:35,815
The appointment has been documented
before setting off,

517
00:37:36,735 --> 00:37:39,415
The border is now in emergency,
and military supplies are pressing,

518
00:37:39,415 --> 00:37:41,535
The assets of Shouyue in Luoyang,

519
00:37:41,535 --> 00:37:43,175
no matter how much money is sold for,

520
00:37:43,175 --> 00:37:46,035
must be offered to the court
in the name of Pei Family of Zhongjuan

521
00:37:46,035 --> 00:37:47,455
to be used as military funds

522
00:37:47,455 --> 00:37:49,535
to fulfill the responsibility of citizens
of the Tang Dynasty

523
00:37:49,535 --> 00:37:51,095
and share the worries of His Majesty,

524
00:38:00,015 --> 00:38:02,215
Pei Shouyue is really audacious,

525
00:38:02,895 --> 00:38:05,155
What gives him the right
to decide this matter by himself?

526
00:38:05,155 --> 00:38:07,495
Today has truly been an eye-opener for me,

527
00:38:09,375 --> 00:38:11,195
Someone is selling his own private property,

528
00:38:11,195 --> 00:38:15,135
and donates it to the court
as a military fund in the name of the clan,

529
00:38:16,095 --> 00:38:19,655
But it's considered as audaciousness
by the court officials of the same clan,

530
00:38:21,215 --> 00:38:24,095
If His Majesty hears these words,

531
00:38:24,855 --> 00:38:27,935
