what Lord Pei and everyone here would do,

532
00:38:31,735 --> 00:38:32,815
I certainly have no such intention,

533
00:38:33,495 --> 00:38:34,615
not even a hint,

534
00:38:36,095 --> 00:38:37,175
This money was well donated,

535
00:38:37,175 --> 00:38:38,415
Really well donated,

536
00:38:38,975 --> 00:38:40,415
Well donated, well donated,

537
00:38:44,775 --> 00:38:47,575
I might have to
shamelessly bother Madam Yang once more,

538
00:38:47,575 --> 00:38:51,495
Please send someone to deliver the 20,000 taels
of gold to the palace,

539
00:38:57,455 --> 00:39:00,215
Lady Wu and I

540
00:39:00,855 --> 00:39:04,855
