to covet others' property,

541
00:39:06,375 --> 00:39:10,175
Lady Wu persuaded me to come here because

542
00:39:10,175 --> 00:39:16,695
she admired the loyalty Liuli and Shouyue have
towards their country and family,

543
00:39:18,175 --> 00:39:22,495
I originally planned
to do good deeds quietly today

544
00:39:23,335 --> 00:39:27,095
